      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、ここがラスベガスのショッピングモールか……\n確かにいろいろでかい気はするけど、結構普通かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ so this is a shopping mall in Las Vegas…\nIt’s true that everything’s huge‚ but it’s kinda normal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 1.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.566666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "その辺歩いてる奴らもカジュアルな感じだし\nラスベガスでも、みんなギラギラって訳でもないのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The people walking around are pretty casual too‚\nand not everyone in Vegas is all glitzy and glamorous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.566666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "っていうか、腰が引けた歩き方いい加減止めろっての\nあんた、アメリカ来たことないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And hey‚ stop walking like you’re scared.\nIs this your first time in America?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "仕事で海外に来たのは、今回が初めてでして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is my first time working overseas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん。ならなおさら、kanaに感謝しなさいよ\nkanaが英語出来るおかげで、通訳もいらないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm. Then you should be even more grateful to me.\nThanks to kana’s English skills‚ we don’t even need an interpreter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.0999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "そもそもkanaの動画がバズったおかげで\nあんたも経費でラスベガスまで来れたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the first place‚ you’re here in Las Vegas\non an expense account because my videos went viral.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね\nそれでkanaさん。このショッピングモールで\nセレブっぽく豪遊するって話でしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that’s true.\nSo‚ kana-san‚ you were saying something about\nflaunting your wealth like celebrities at this shopping mall…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
